name: ARGHTEE - HYPE YOUR NFT by STEPHEN HUTCHINS
description: Collaboration between the NFT Hypeman "Arghtee" and the maestro himself "Stephen Hutchins". Piece originally planned as use in promotion for the Hypeman in a campaign to onboard more artists to the Tezos Blockchain and "hicetnunc", and for general song awareness for "Hype Your NFT", the NFT song from Arghtee.
